title: Judge Dredd Megazine (v1 - present) (ongoing) (- Nem -)
description:
In the dystopian post-apocalyptic future of the 22nd century, crime runs rampant in Mega-City One. Here the people are policed by the Judges, elite cops prepared to do whatever it takes to keep the peace, even if it means sentencing criminals to death on the spot!

The five volumes entitled Judge Dredd: The Megazine (a sister title to 2000AD). 

    Volume 1: issues 1-20 (1-20)
    Volume 2: issues 1-83 (21-103)
    Volume 3: issues 1-79 (104-182)
    Volume 4: issues 1-18 (183-200)
    Volume 5 is ongoing and starts with issue 201
